    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "תּם might even be taken as neuter for תּם, and ישׂר for ישׁר; but in this case the poet would have written רעה instead of ראה; שׁמר is therefore used as, e.g., in ",
