        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". By כּי that to which attention is specially called is introduced. The man of peace has a totally different lot from the evil-doer who delights in contention and persecution. As the fruit of his love of peace he has אחרית, a future, ",
